Lord, maybe you've impressed upon someone's heart this evening.

741
00:39:48,080 --> 00:39:50,080
Maybe we're not worshiping you like we should.

742
00:39:50,080 --> 00:39:54,080
Maybe we don't see you in your rightful place, high, holy, and lifted up.

743
00:39:54,080 --> 00:39:57,080
God, would you move and work in hearts and lives as only you can.

744
00:39:57,080 --> 00:39:58,080
And we'll thank you for it.

745
00:39:58,080 --> 00:39:59,080
In Christ's name we pray.

746
00:39:59,080 --> 00:40:00,080
Would you stand up?

747
00:40:00,080 --> 00:40:00,920
with me.

